{"tid":1285331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[資安101] 湯家驊話香港失去咗法治 我地要點保護自己?","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:03.000Z","uid":68772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4818eb185035fd8b0b674e5f1c917647828964e4","tid":1285331,"uid":68772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"學湯家驊話齋「這將是歷史上被視為香港失去法治的一天」<br />\n我諗各位巴絲都睇到香港變得越黎越危險<br />\n喺呢啲非常時期 每個人都要學識保護自己手機、電腦同埋啲accounts啲個人資料<br />\n對抗黃屍 人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n知道好多人都比較懶 所以我淨係想透過個人經驗做個小小嘅整合<br />\n呢到講嘅嘢都係啲好基本同好簡單嘅嘢 等大家比較容易入口 最緊要係慢慢建立啲私隱同埋安全意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係高手可以唔洗睇 但麻煩幫手推推po 或者睇下有冇補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 保持軟件更新</strong></span></span><br />\nKeep住啲software係up tp date呢點好緊要 因為每次軟件更新除咗加新功能至於 仲要好緊要嘅security patch<br />\n即係話如果你用緊嘅軟件越舊咁你俾人hack嘅風險亦都越高<br />\n唔update嘅話有幾大鑊？可以睇下過去嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n<code>Google Chrome爆重大遠端程式碼漏洞，已有攻擊程式流傳| iThome</code><br />\n<code>微軟修補64個安全漏洞，當中兩個已遭開採| iThome</code><br />\n<code>Android藏重大漏洞，用戶只要點擊PNG圖片就可能遭受遠端攻擊| iThome</code><br />\n<code>Google修補Android 11項重大及高風險安全漏洞| iThome</code><br />\n<code>蘋果釋出iOS 12.2以修補51個安全漏洞| iThome</code><br />\n<code>臉書緊急修補WhatsApp被駭客開採的漏洞| iThome</code><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Google search: <em>漏洞 site:<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=57e7fa2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw</a></em></span><br />\n<br />\n用緊iPhone 6嘅恭喜你 你部機9月前都仲可以update到最新version<br />\nandroid嘅話 一般黎講啲廠support 2-3年嘅update 自己check返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. 唔好隨便grant權限</strong></span></span><br />\n- contacts: 入面避免入啲個人資料：例如地址、密碼等等<br />\n- location: 如非必要都唔好俾permission，iPhone嘅話較返&rdquo;while using&rdquo; 甚至&rdquo;never&rdquo;<br />\n- photos: 啲相入面有太多個人資料 好輕易可以知道你個人生活同埋去過邊啲地方 盡量都唔好share， iPhone有啲app如果有得揀揀返&rdquo;add photos only&rdquo;<br />\n- camera: 有啲app影咗你相都未必知 小心!<br />\n- microphone: 同樣都係比較敏感 特別係android：好似可以隨時喺背景錄音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3. 盡量都開2FA</strong></span></span><br />\n2FA (Two factor authentication)<br />\n呢樣好緊要 最近都聽有唔少人Telegram、Twitter俾人login<br />\n整咗2FA 好處係login嗰時佢除咗問你密碼之外仲要拎code 多重保障<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>Follow左連登twitter嘅你 入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284635</a></em></span><br />\n<br />\nSMS之前爆過LTE有漏洞可以俾hacker截取訊息，極唔建議用黎做2FA同埋拎login code，更何況電訊商仲可以睇到曬你啲嘢<br />\n推介返Microsoft Authenticator app黎gen code<br />\n好處係可以backup上Microsoft account，唔驚唔見電話冇曬啲code<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/account/authenticator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Faccount%2Fauthenticator&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=39e4808f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/account/authenticator</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">**Telegram, WhatsApp, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook都有2FA功能</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4. 唔好重複用同一個密碼</strong></span></span><br />\n點解成日話唔好重複使用密碼？咪因為一個密碼有太多機會可能洩漏 例如你喺人地部機login過你Google acc，而佢部電腦咁裝咗個木馬程式；或者某個網站俾人hack咗 而你密碼咁啱被洩漏咗出黎<br />\n唔係要你記曬咁多密碼 不過你可以用password manager幫你<br />\n推介返用LastPass（免費功能好齊） 或者1Password<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過小心謹記 password manager嘅密碼自己要小心保管好(唔好寫出黎) 如果leak咗咁你全部acc都俾人睇到曬</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 注意自己留咗咩資料喺手機/網上</span></span></strong><br />\n- Google會儲存你去過邊啲地方、search過啲咩、上過咩網、開過咩app(android only)甚至你嗌Google assistant啲錄音 <br />\n<br />\n如果擔心洩漏行蹤建議turn off返Web &amp; App Activity同埋Location History<br />\n<a href=\"https://myaccount.google.com/activitycontrols?pli=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyaccount.google.com%2Factivitycontrols%3Fpli%3D1&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bc6ab764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myaccount.google.com/activitycontrols?pli=1</a><br />\n可以參考：<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-location-tracking-turn-off-iphone-android-2018-8#next-click-on-google-account-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-location-tracking-turn-off-iphone-android-2018-8%23next-click-on-google-account-4&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=67ce9e6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.businessinsider.com/google-location-tracking-turn-off-iphone-android-2018-8#next-click-on-google-account-4</a><br />\n<br />\n- iOS喺location storage都有個位置紀錄你去過邊啲地方<br />\n想睇返可以去:setting -&gt; privacy -&gt; location service -&gt; system service -&gt; significant locations<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 加密手機/電腦</span></strong></span><br />\n- iPhone有曬加密 但記得要set返個可靠嘅密碼 建議用英文字母同數字組成嘅長密碼<br />\n- android唔清楚 要睇返部機setting<br />\n- macOS嘅話開返FileVault<br />\n- windows 嘅話參考返：<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">[重要] 電腦電話加密!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7. 唔好隨便拎部電話\\電腦去插USB或者電腦</span></span></strong><br />\n插USB係最容易中毒嘅一個途徑之一<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大陸已經發生過有人charge個電 手機都俾人裝曬木馬 呢啲嘢難保香港唔會發生 所以各位小心</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20170725003275-260804?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fhottopic%2F20170725003275-260804%3Fchdtv&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=699729da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20170725003275-260804?chdtv</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8. 避免安裝可疑軟件</span></strong></span><br />\n除咗有洩漏資料/被hack風險外 更加唔好成為黑客攻擊嘅幫凶<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">史無前例！46萬支中國手機發動DDoS洪水攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9. 睇清楚條link先好開</span></span></strong><br />\n不言而喻<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yWuE5Lz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyWuE5Lz.png&h=4740edc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10861ad85542f6631ce477f289ff00a4fad33943","tid":1285331,"uid":68772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"諗到再加<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4d497fec30993f88d795d8d9105c554a600b4b","tid":1285331,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f6e9ff61e7884f1e4fbb631491a887a1055042e","tid":1285331,"uid":68772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:03:33.000Z"